Notes:
Background-color property only applies to padding and content.

Can combine padding properties into one.
Padding: 20px 20px 20px 70px;  (top, right, bottom padding are 20px, and left pa dding is 70px)
padding: 10px 40px;   (top and bottom padding are 10px, right and left padding are 40px)
Padding: 20px;  (top, right, bottom and left padding are 20px)

Can combine border properties too.
border: black 2px solid;   (border-color, border-width, and border-style)

To eliminate margin.
body{
Margin: 0; 
}
